[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0059","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0059.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0018","title":"IBM AIX、SCO Unixware、SGI IRIX、Sun Solaris statd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"statd 服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制 RPC 请求，触发 statd 守护进程中的缓冲区溢出，进而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 3.2/4.1、SCO Unixware 7.1.1、SGI IRIX 5.3 及 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 等多款 Unix 操作系统，利用方式为网络远程攻击，无需身份认证。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0018"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.700","remediation":"立即安装各厂商提供的 rpc.statd 补丁包：Sun Solaris 2.5.1 安装 Sun 补丁 ID 105402-02 或更新版本；IBM AIX 4.1 安装 APAR IX64628；SGI IRIX 5.3 安装 SGI 安全补丁 19970801-01-P。如系统已停止维护，应升级到受支持的操作系统版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上禁止外部访问 portmap（TCP/UDP 111）和 rpc.statd 使用的动态端口（通常为 32771/4045），或停止 rpc.statd 服务（`/etc/init.d/rpc.statd stop`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/127","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19104","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0018.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0018","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0018.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0018.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2p8f-w9gg-hwrc/GHSA-2p8f-w9gg-hwrc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/rpc_statd.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0059.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0559","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0559.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0340","title":"Slackware Linux crond 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux Slackware 系统中 crond 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户可通过向 crond 程序发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞允许拥有本地账户的攻击者利用 crond 在处理参数时的内存边界校验缺陷，实现权限提升。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，影响 Slackware Linux 系统。建议用户升级至修复版本或限制本地用户对 crond 的访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0340"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.243","remediation":"升级 Slackware Linux 至 3.4 及以上版本，该修复版本已修正 crond 程序在处理用户提交的计划任务参数时的边界检查缺陷，防止本地用户通过特制参数触发缓冲区溢出提权。如无法升级，可限制 crond 仅允许受信用户通过 `cron.allow` 文件控制访问，并移除 `/etc/cron.d` 中不必要的任务文件。同时检查 crond 二进制是否被替换，使用 `rpm -V` 或 `md5sum` 校验文件完整性。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0340"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0559.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0429","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0429.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0244","title":"Livingston RADIUS 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Livingston RADIUS 实现存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向 RADIUS 认证服务发送特制数据包触发缓冲区溢出，导致以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响多个 Livingston 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级至最新版本或部署访问控制列表限制 RADIUS 服务访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0244"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.367","remediation":"立即升级 Livingston RADIUS 至 2.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 RADIUS 代码中的栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。对于无法升级的旧系统，应在边界防火墙上限制对 RADIUS UDP 端口 1812/1645 的访问来源，仅允许受信任的 NAS 设备 IP 接入。建议迁移至当前仍受支持的 RADIUS 实现（如 FreeRADIUS 3.x），并在运行 RADIUS 服务的主机上启用栈缓冲区溢出保护机制（如 ASLR、NX）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0244","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0244.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0244","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0244.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4912a395-3fc6-4764-84b7-7d315af3698f.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0429.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0376","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0376.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0193","title":"3Com 路由器 TCP 零长选项拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ascend 与 3Com 路由器在处理特殊构造的 TCP 数据包时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标路由器发送包含零长度 TCP 选项（Zero Length TCP Option）的恶意数据包，触发设备处理异常导致路由器强制重启或崩溃。该漏洞影响 Ascend R 4.5 Ci12 及部分 3Com 路由器版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。目前厂商已发布固件更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0193"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:52.973","remediation":"建议升级 Ascend Router 固件至 4.5 Ci12 之后的修复版本，或升级 3Com 路由器至厂商发布的修补固件。若暂时无法升级，可在边界防火墙配置规则丢弃 TCP 选项长度为 0 的异常数据包，同时启用 TCP 状态检测功能缓解攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0193","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20332","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0193","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0193.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5p2w-742f-cg75/GHSA-5p2w-742f-cg75.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000239.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0376.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0056","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0056.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0016","title":"多厂商 TCP Land 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Land 攻击是一种经典的拒绝服务攻击方式。攻击者向目标主机发送一个特制的 TCP SYN 数据包，其中源 IP 地址、源端口与目的 IP 地址、目的端口完全相同。目标主机收到后试图与自己建立 TCP 连接，导致操作系统陷入无限自应答循环，最终耗尽 CPU 资源造成系统崩溃或挂起。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0、Linux 2.0.34 以下版本、FreeBSD 2.2.6 以下版本、HP-UX、NetBSD 等多个主流操作系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0016"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到已修复版本：Windows NT 4.0 安装 Service Pack 4 及以上，Linux 升级内核至 2.0.34 及以上，FreeBSD 升级至 2.2.6 及以上，NetBSD 升级至 1.3.2 及以上，HP-UX 安装对应 PHNE 补丁。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙/路由器上配置 ACL 策略，丢弃源 IP 与目的 IP 相同的入站 TCP SYN 数据包，同时启用基于 RFC 2827 的入口过滤以防止 IP 地址欺骗。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9801-076","https://security.netapp.com/advisory/ntap-20170815-0001/","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20814","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0016.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/1fb9a053a31c41206e693c4b4856611d722d4df7/1999/CVE-1999-0016.json","https://github.com/mthcht/awesome-lists/blob/20bccdfe36ad7e2a6c15ebfa83f10e46b5864396/Lists/Others/Defender_yara_rules/Win32/Exploit/CVE-1999-0016.yara","https://github.com/roadwy/DefenderYara/blob/59e39903d9e6667c7c3e55a1f2887f1faab0e423/Exploit/Win32/CVE-1999-0016/Exploit_Win32_CVE-1999-0016_MR_MTB.yar","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/bef4442939206e97bbfee4995afab3b6c8a2377c/1999/CVE-1999-0016/README.md","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0016","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/c8b30957414aefbd6ba0b766db0d40593ba36fba/references/CVE-1999-0016-2023-09-21-1730","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/diannaofengzi/POC/blob/14d504f7488db9229f6f02be54aab53e3cfee0dc/databases/1999/database/CVE-1999-0016/CVE-1999-0016-POC-Pommaq.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest/blob/8829fba0b0ee59d68a105191067da3a7b4aa27de/references/contrib1-CVE-1999-0016-2025-03-17-1422","https://github.com/pexmee/CVE-1999-0016-Land-DOS-tool","https://github.com/Pommaq/CVE-1999-0016-POC"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0056.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1429","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1429.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1257","title":"Xyplex Terminal Server 安全绕过漏洞","description":"Xyplex 终端服务器 6.0.1S1 及可能其他版本存在安全绕过漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过在登录密码提示符处输入 CTRL-Z 字符或问号(?)即可绕过认证机制，从而未授权获取终端服务器访问权限。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，影响系统机密性、完整性和可用性。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1257"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-11-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.183","remediation":"联系厂商获取最新固件版本，或在终端服务器配置中禁用特殊字符（CTRL-Z、问号）透传，启用强密码认证机制。如设备已停止支持，建议在网络边界部署访问控制列表（ACL），仅允许受信 IP 访问终端服务器端口，并在传输层启用 SSH 替代 Telnet 以消除明文认证绕过风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/8134","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1825","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1826","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1257.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1257","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1257.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1257.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x5qw-j8m6-38mj/GHSA-x5qw-j8m6-38mj.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1257.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--948185a2-65fd-4e22-96bc-ab4110bc58d1.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1429.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0396","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0396.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0210","title":"Sun Microsystems Solaris automountd 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.5.1 系统中的自动挂载守护进程 automountd 存在 shell 元字符注入漏洞，本地或远程攻击者可通过向 automountd 传递包含特殊 shell 字符的恶意请求，诱使系统以提升的权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.5.1 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击者无需身份认证即可触发利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0210"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-11-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.103","remediation":"立即安装 Sun 官方补丁：Solaris 2.5.1 SPARC 平台安装 103613-01 或更新版本，x86 平台安装 103612-01 或更新版本；Solaris 2.6 用户安装对应内核补丁。如无法立即升级，可在 `/etc/init.d/autofs` 中停止 automountd 服务并禁用自启动（`/etc/init.d/autofs stop; rm /etc/rc3.d/S74autofs`），同时在 `/etc/hosts.equiv` 和 `netgroup` 中限制可访问 automount 资源的主机范围作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88053459921223&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91547759121289&w=2","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-99-05-statd-automountd.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/235","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9910-104","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19199","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0210.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0210.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0210","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0210.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0210.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-63gj-m3j5-p47q/GHSA-63gj-m3j5-p47q.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/rpc_automountd.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0396.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1397","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1397.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1209","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9085,\"outputTokens\":25,\"totalTokens\":10838}}","description":"SCO OpenServer 5.0 及 SCO Open Desktop/Open Server 3.0 的 scoterm 组件存在权限许可和访问控制漏洞，本地攻击者可利用 scoterm 组件的权限配置缺陷，通过特定操作提升权限获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer 5.0 及 SCO Open Desktop/Open Server 3.0 版本，攻击者需具备本地访问权限，利用 scoterm 组件的权限配置缺陷实现本地提权，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1209"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-11-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:57.147","remediation":"建议升级 scoterm 至 SCO 官方发布的已修复版本，或应用厂商提供的安全补丁。若暂无法升级，应移除 scoterm 程序的 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/scoterm），或通过文件权限限制仅授权用户执行，以阻断本地用户借此提权至 root。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88131151000069&w=2","http://www.cert.org/vendor_bulletins/VB-97.14.scoterm","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/690"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1397.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1398","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1398.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1210","title":"Digital UNIX xterm 符号链接任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Digital UNIX 4.0B 打补丁包 5 的 xterm 存在本地任意文件写入漏洞。当 xterm 在 DISPLAY 环境变量设置为无法访问的显示设备时被调用，会创建核心转储文件，本地攻击者可通过符号链接攻击该核心转储文件覆盖系统任意文件。攻击者需具备本地访问权限且能控制 DISPLAY 环境变量，利用符号链接将核心转储重定向至敏感文件路径实现任意文件覆盖，CVSS 评分 7.2，属高危本地权限提升漏洞。影响 Digital UNIX 4.0B 补丁包 5 版本的 xterm 组件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1210"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-11-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:57.263","remediation":"建议立即移除 /usr/bin/X11/xterm 的 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xterm），并引导用户改用 dxterm 作为替代终端。Digital UNIX 4.0B 补丁包 5 引入的 xterm 替换版本存在该缺陷，卸载补丁包 5 或回滚至未打补丁的 xterm 版本可彻底修复。如无法立即回滚，设置核心转储目录限制（ulimit -c 0 或配置 core_pattern 限制写入目录）可作为临时缓解措施防止符号链接攻击覆盖系统文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87936891504885&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/613","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7e65fa522cff0172990568230ff9b719b8650296/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1210.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1210","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1210.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6fc85c731fb3018b2c4fbe9aed66186edd5321b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1210.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rx4w-gvh4-qffg/GHSA-rx4w-gvh4-qffg.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88938/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1210.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--6dd60685-4205-4be1-9eda-b8523ea6b2a4.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1398.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1234","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1234.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1069","title":"iCat Carbo Server 目录遍历漏洞","description":"iCat Carbo Server 3.0.0 中的 carbo.dll 组件存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向 icatcommand 参数传递包含 `../` 序列的恶意请求，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件，导致数据库配置、源代码等敏感信息泄露。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，影响 iCat Electronic Commerce Suite 3.0 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1069"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-11-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:39.400","remediation":"iCat Carbo Server 3.0.0 已停止维护，厂商不再提供安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的电子商务平台（如 Magento、Shopify 等）。如无法迁移，可在 Web 服务器（IIS/Apache）层面添加 URL 重写规则，拦截 icatcommand 参数中包含 ../ 或 ..%2f 等目录遍历序列的请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/7943","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2126","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1620","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20513"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1234.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0068","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0068.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0021","title":"Muhammad A. Muquit wwwcount 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"wwwcount 的 Count.cgi 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 Web 服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致任意命令执行。该漏洞影响 wwwcount 2.3 及更早版本，攻击无需身份认证，危害等级高，CVSS 评分 7.5。通过向 Count.cgi 传入超长参数即可触发栈溢出，从而实现远程代码执行或拒绝服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0021"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-11-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:22.013","remediation":"升级 wwwcount 至 2.4 及以上版本，或从 CGI 目录移除 Count.cgi 脚本。若无法升级，在 Web 服务器层面添加输入过滤规则，限制对 Count.cgi 的参数长度（如 Apache ModSecurity 限制 QUERY_STRING 不超过 256 字节），并确保以最低权限运行 CGI 程序。同时可在 Web 服务器访问控制中限制 Count.cgi 仅允许信任的来源 IP 调用，降低被远程利用的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/128","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19105","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0021.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0021","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0021.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0021.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0021.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jfr4-hpqv-2pq4/GHSA-jfr4-hpqv-2pq4.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/count_cgi.nasl","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/1149.txt","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0068.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0511","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0511.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0306","title":"HP-UX xlock 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 系统中的 xlock 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可以通过向 xlock 程序发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，导致攻击者能够以 root 权限执行任意代码，从而完全控制受影响的系统。攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0306"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-11-04","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 系统至包含安全补丁的最新版本，限制非授权用户对 xlock 程序的执行权限，并监控系统日志中的异常提权行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T12:15:41.755870705+00:00","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0306"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0511.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0542","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0542.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0327","title":"SGI IRIX syserr 本地文件破坏漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统的 syserr 程序存在文件处理缺陷，本地攻击者可利用该程序以系统权限破坏或覆盖任意文件，导致系统不稳定或拒绝服务。该漏洞仅需本地用户账户即可触发，无需特殊权限，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0327"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.697","remediation":"立即应用 SGI 安全公告 19971103-01-PX 提供的官方补丁。由于 SGI IRIX 已于 2013 年底停止技术支持，长期建议迁移至仍在维护的 Linux 或 BSD 操作系统。临时缓解措施：以 root 身份执行 `chmod 755 /usr/sbin/syserr` 移除 setuid 权限位，并通过 `chgrp` 将 syserr 程序组改为仅受信任的管理员组，限制普通用户执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0542.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0403","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0403.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0216","title":"Linux Kernel inetd SYN/RST Packet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.6.20.1 版本的 inetd 超级服务守护进程存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标主机发送特制的 SYN 和 RST 数据包，导致 inetd 服务异常终止或资源耗尽，无法正常响应合法连接请求。该漏洞影响运行 inetd 服务的 Linux 系统，攻击者无需认证即可实施攻击，且无需目标系统上存在特定监听服务。利用方式简单，通过发送大量伪造的 TCP SYN/RST 包即可触发，属于典型的网络层拒绝服务攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0216"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.917","remediation":"建议将 legacy inetd 替换为 xinetd，并在配置中设置 per_source = 5、cps = 25 30、max_load = 3 以限制并发连接和速率。或者迁移至 systemd socket 激活机制，利用内核 SYN cookies（sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_syncookies=1）和 iptables/nftables 限制入站 SYN 包速率（如 iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --syn -m limit --limit 10/s -j ACCEPT）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0216","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0216","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0216.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g7qq-2qq9-j34m/GHSA-g7qq-2qq9-j34m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2bbcf0ff-3ba8-4c91-aea6-e3d5fdb0e178.json","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/linux.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0403.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0543","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0543.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0328","title":"SGI IRIX permissions 程序缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 5.x 和 6.x 系统中 /usr/lib/desktop/permissions 程序存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向该程序提供超长且精心构造的第4个参数，触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 sys 组权限执行任意代码。该漏洞已有公开利用代码，由 David Hedley 于 1997年5月发布。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0328"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-11-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即应用 SGI 安全公告 19971103-01-PX 中提供的补丁，升级 permissions 程序。如无法打补丁，应移除 permissions 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/lib/desktop/permissions），并严格限制可登录系统的本地用户账号，仅保留受信任的管理员用户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0328","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19318"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19318"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0543.toml"}]